## Getting Started

1. Download the appropriate `.xlsx` files from Cognito Forms and SalesForce (note that SalesForce file must be exported as an unformatted `.xlsx`).
2. Download the most up to date [release](https://github.com/The-Compass-LCOC/scripts-shopping-list/releases) in this Repository.
3. Unzip the file to it's own folder.
4. Drop the files from Cognito Forms and SalesForce renaming them to `Shopping List.xlsx` and `Arrival Time Detail Report.xlsx`.
5. Double click on `shopping-list-mail-merge.vbs`.
6. Wait, select the correct table and press okay when prompted, continue waiting only the Arrival Time Detail Report and Form Letters1 windows are left.